name: fg-assignment-01
description:
Assignment 1 Project

Strategy

Targeted audience are elementary level students (ie. Lower Primary School Students) or students that are just introduced into the 4 basic mathematical operations. This is to exercise and train on the mathematical skill set of the user in both quick-thinking and working underpressure. The attractive and bright pixel art along with the cheerful and catchy music appeals to the intended demographic, inciting them to use the application often. Perhaps even inciting competitiveness between their peers with the built in high-score system.
